        @RabbitListener(queues="BatchData-Queue")
public void recievedMessage(NewBatch newBatch)
        Receives data from RabbitMQ messaging queue, and stores the data in an instance of NewBatch. This data is extracted and stored into Associate, Batch, Employee, and EmployeeBatch instances, which are then persisted into the database.
